Class SnmpFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.nsx.node.services.snmp.SnmpFactory

  • public class SnmpFactory
extends Object
    SnmpFactory is responsible for creating instances of services contained inside the com.vmware.nsx.node.services.snmp package and also has the subpackages reference to access respective subpackage services.
